1
00:00:07,374 --> 00:00:09,511
You even look good
while you're sleeping.

2
00:00:10,311 --> 00:00:12,879
Like you're ready for a photoshoot.

3
00:00:17,083 --> 00:00:17,951
Cousin...

4
00:00:17,952 --> 00:00:19,318
I'll work harder from now on.

5
00:00:19,319 --> 00:00:20,153
I won't slack off.

6
00:00:20,154 --> 00:00:21,588
I'll always remember my place.

7
00:00:35,702 --> 00:00:36,736
What are you doing here?

8
00:00:37,737 --> 00:00:38,897
We're supposed to be working,

9
00:00:39,039 --> 00:00:40,039
remember?

10
00:00:49,082 --> 00:00:51,217
You usually wear your hair up.

11
00:00:52,318 --> 00:00:53,319
With it down like this,

12
00:00:53,820 --> 00:00:54,988
you look like a student.

13
00:00:56,890 --> 00:00:58,124
So, which do you prefer?

14
00:00:58,958 --> 00:01:00,360
It doesn't matter what I like.

15
00:01:01,060 --> 00:01:02,327
What matters is

16
00:01:02,328 --> 00:01:03,930
what your fans like.

17
00:01:06,366 --> 00:01:07,366
By the way,

18
00:01:07,634 --> 00:01:08,501
I checked your social media.

19
00:01:08,502 --> 00:01:10,170
Why is it all work stuff?

20
00:01:10,770 --> 00:01:12,772
Post more personal stuff.

21
00:01:13,540 --> 00:01:14,540
You actually checked?

22
00:01:15,308 --> 00:01:16,042
If I didn't,

23
00:01:16,043 --> 00:01:17,977
you'd nag me for being unprofessional.

24
00:01:20,139 --> 00:01:21,941
Here, eat this.

25
00:01:28,321 --> 00:01:30,041
You're still not being professional enough.

26
00:01:30,557 --> 00:01:31,825
I don't eat green onions.

27
00:01:33,693 --> 00:01:35,493
I didn't have time to
catch up on everything.

28
00:01:38,231 --> 00:01:39,631
You need to put your heart into it.

29
00:01:39,933 --> 00:01:41,234
Don't just memorize the facts.

30
00:01:42,102 --> 00:01:43,369
Fine...

31
00:01:43,703 --> 00:01:45,070
Just eat it already.

32
00:01:45,071 --> 00:01:45,872
You'll get better faster,

33
00:01:45,873 --> 00:01:46,913
and you won't get me sick.

34
00:02:03,123 --> 00:02:04,691
I know you don't like sweets,

35
00:02:05,091 --> 00:02:06,593
but this will mask the taste.

36
00:02:15,301 --> 00:02:16,301
But...

37
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,138
I have a question.

38
00:02:18,938 --> 00:02:20,405
There's only one

39
00:02:20,406 --> 00:02:21,941
queen bed in here.

40
00:02:22,542 --> 00:02:24,644
It looks like we really have to share it.
